{"tid":2140030,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【炒家勁蝕】內地客輸到七彩　斷供走人　多個物業淪為銀主盤","createTime":"2020-08-04T16:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T23:06:03.000Z","uid":28114,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5f376d7eac65100221b6adb45cfdf9514d307d","tid":2140030,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2710000/2714853/POLIMUTFF_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2710000%2F2714853%2FPOLIMUTFF_600.png&h=6f63d9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去數年，內地資金缺乏出路，加上人民幣貶值，不少炒家來港炒樓，主攻豪宅市場。可是，早前中美爆發貿易戰，加上疫情肆虐，對香港豪宅影響深遠，終致部分內地炒家蝕讓離場。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，北角柏蔚山3座低層G室，實用面積911平方呎，於2018年6月，以2,861萬元購入。可是，今年一月，業主斷供，遭銀行收樓，物業因此淪成銀主盤。銀行收樓後，曾以2,800萬元放售該豪宅，惟市道差，單位遲遲未能易手，終累減近兩成，以2,300萬元沽出，實用呎價25,247元，低市價逾一成。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主姓許，為內地炒家，多年前在香港掃貨，動用逾億元購入多伙豪宅，包括北角柏傲山、北角柏傲山、何文田天鑄、何文田皓畋、以及南昌站匯璽等，最終財困斷供，其中幾伙豪宅慘成銀主盤。有代理透露，現已找不到這位炒家，又坦言這位炒家可算見證豪宅市場興衰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2714853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2714853&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeat5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=70fe3b78\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2714853</a>"},{"pid":"ac00c6994fb1751ceca2bbcf8a9f02dd5b107f2e","tid":2140030,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"有黨安法，驚西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53921995d761371868fa4ed42f99b5677fe8379d","tid":2140030,"uid":15605,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"基本法賦予樓價升，驚閪"},{"pid":"6bdc5c04c1be7a1892f44f3acb6e920513613501","tid":2140030,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">其中幾伙豪宅慘成銀主盤</span></blockquote>有幾慘？白事當紅事辦啦 支那style<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94696205bf62ca311e880f5656e2f79726bb4da","tid":2140030,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"出得來行，你估唔駛還"},{"pid":"cc601ab9d734294b0de01321986fdc9b18f1235c","tid":2140030,"uid":268053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:08:05.000Z","msg":"銀主極都係唔值呢個價，香港樓根本唔值呢個價"},{"pid":"b2d719e7351841b6b8b2d5756521cd8398ba5d20","tid":2140030,"uid":261171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"有代理透露，現已找不到這位炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ceacb8f3c60aac2df3da6203b1a4dd164c843e5","tid":2140030,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"傻撚左先會兩千幾萬買個單位仔"},{"pid":"53a53b94fc7a6576b26168ad34309a75824e1751","tid":2140030,"uid":7057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"竟然仲有人用2300入市。"},{"pid":"d85a18f5d1a7381e0b867a9f752489bd152c9ddf","tid":2140030,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"炒家點會買豪宅炒<br />\n根本佢就係落嚟買豪宅二按，借咗銀行錢唔還走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fbab89ee6cb48f2f12d714cef04a5c2a2c1c0b","tid":2140030,"uid":351671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2d719e7351841b6b8b2d5756521cd8398ba5d20","tid":2140030,"uid":261171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"有代理透露，現已找不到這位炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"武肺死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703da005f208d894594c207ee32134e4bf5672b5","tid":2140030,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85a18f5d1a7381e0b867a9f752489bd152c9ddf","tid":2140030,"uid":470